portfolioDeployed(string,bytes32,address.details: Emitted when a Portfolio (contract) is deployed with createPortfolio method and create2.

portfolioRegistered(string,bytes32,addre.details: Emitted when a Portfolio (contract address) is added to the Portfolios Registered array.

portfolioSupportAdded(string,bytes32).details: Emitted when a Portfolio (bytecode hash) is added to the map of Portfolios Supported.

portfolioSupportDeleted(string,bytes32).details: Emitted when a Portfolio (bytecode hash) is deleted from the map of Portfolios Supported.

portfolioUnregistered(address,address).details: Emitted when a Portfolio (contract address) is removed from the Portfolios Registered array.

addPortfolioSupport(string,bytes32).details: Add support of a Portfolio. Requirements: onlyOwner.

params.hashCreationCode_: creation byte code Hash of Portfolio contract to be added.

createPortfolio(bytes,address,string,str.details: Create a Portfolio using the provided byte code (create2) and regiter it (Factory and Registry patterns). Requirements: whenNotPaused and portfolio byte code is supported.

params.owner_: address of owner of portfolio - Transfer ownership of Portfolio created to owner_.
params.portfolioByteCode_: creation byte code of Portfolio contract to be created. Hash of byte code must be supported by Registry.
params.portoflioURI_: URI of Portfolio (Current Client implementation: IPFS CID of image file).

delPortfolioSupport(string,bytes32).details: Delete support of a Portfolio and emits event 'portfolioSupportDeleted' if successful.Requirements: onlyOwner.

params.contractName_: Name of Portfolio Contract to be deleted.
params.hashCreationCode_: creation byte code Hash of Portfolio contract to be deleted.

returns._0: boolean - False if Portfolio hash not in the list of supported Portfolios.

getAllPortofliosRegistered().details: Get registered Portfolios' addresses (array). Requirements: whenNotPaused.

getHashByteCode(bytes).details: Compute keccak256 Hash of bytecode provided.

params.byteCode_: creation byte code of Portfolio contract to be created.

isPortoflioRegistered(address).details: Verify if Portfolio registred by checking the '_portfoliosRegisteredIndex'.

params.portfolioAddress: address of Portfolio to be verified.

returns._0: boolean - False if Portfolio not registered.

isPortoflioSupported(string,bytes32).details: Verify if Portfolio supported by checking the hash and name of creationCode in the mapping '_portfoliosSupported'.

params.contractName_: Name of Portfolio Contract to be verified.
params.hashCreationCode_: creation byte code Hash of Portfolio contract to be verified.

returns._0: boolean - False if Portfolio hash not in the list of supported Portfolios.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

paused().details: Returns true if the contract is paused, and false otherwise.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

unregisterPortfolio(address).details: Unregister a Portfolio at address specified.Requirements: whenNotPaused and called by owner of Portfolio or Registry only.

params.portfolioAddress: address of Portfolio to be unregistered.
